name: Devon Walker
bio: Devon Walker performs in Austin, TX near where he grew up. Devon was recently featured on the Moontower Comedy Festival, and was named a Semi-Finalist in the Funniest Person in Austin Competition. Devon has a Master's degree in a field that nobody knows about. Devon doesn't really like writing bios about himself. Come support his shows so that he can pursue his dreams of having someone else write bios for him.
